data.name: textBoxDescription.Text
data.value:
Credits: CaitSith2 - Total reverse engineering of the Denpa Men QR code format.
Eli Sherer - For the pushmo level editor, which was used as the base for this program. (Mainly, for dealing with the use of the ZXing QR code library)
Be.HexEditor - For the hex editor control, which was a great help in hacking the QR code format.
Genius Sonority Inc. - For localizing this awesome game, and for not making the QR code format too complex.
http://wikiwiki.jp/denpaningen/ - Full list of japanese names for the random denpa function, when region is set for Japan.
